title: Man injured on Mount Pilchuck
text:
Search and rescue and air support are responding at Mount Pilchuck for a report of an injured man.
The Snohomish County Sheriff’s Office helicopter, SnoHAWK, is heading to the mountain to help locate the man.
The extent of the victim’s injuries and his exact location are not yet known.
